{"tid":1914362,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"今個禮拜就快做爸爸媽媽既你請入","createTime":"2020-03-07T13:04:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-07T13:26:02.000Z","uid":248120,"like":7,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"0d965556864c9ed5d6259914767d8a5a50976aac","tid":1914362,"uid":248120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-07T13:04:31.000Z","msg":"老老實實：<br />\n你地係咪6月9號個日一齊訓過覺？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n係既話⋯⋯<br />\n我要先多謝你一齊同我地行到今日。<br />\n<br />\n你可能已經淡出手足圈<br />\n亦可能已經無左當日個份熱情<br />\n但係離個一日，已經有9個月<br />\n正常來講，9個月足以孕育一個新既生命<br />\n但對於孕育民主自由既香港而言，或言之過早<br />\n<br />\n重要既係<br />\n你想俾一個點既香港俾佢？<br />\n你想佢聽到點樣既香港歷史？<br />\n你想傳承乜野既回憶俾佢？<br />\n<br />\n所以各位手足，<br />\n有你呢9個月以來、以及以後既努力<br />\n絕對唔會令新既生命承受獨裁政權既荼毒<br />\n<br />\n6月9日既種子<br />\n呢一兩日應該會開花<br />\n而跟住既「結果」，由你話事<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0edace0c05f6acb8f450bb0b3b3800c5b7a08edc","tid":1914362,"uid":199893,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-07T13:06:20.000Z","msg":"你點會無啦啦意識到呢啲嘢...<br />\n正常都唔會諗"},{"pid":"428adae699bd49285e8c975b593294d407e10b8c","tid":1914362,"uid":11598,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"0edace0c05f6acb8f450bb0b3b3800c5b7a08edc","tid":1914362,"uid":199893,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-07T13:06:20.000Z","msg":"你點會無啦啦意識到呢啲嘢...<br />\n正常都唔會諗"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-07T13:23:47.000Z","msg":"佢就係6月9日嘅種子"},{"pid":"4ae8846d07516d16cd22a5b074c4a4c995157e06","tid":1914362,"uid":203628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-07T13:26:02.000Z","msg":"準喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}